data.description: Welcome Home! This 3-bedroom, 2 1/2-bath home is a canvas waiting for your personal touch. This property is situated in a well-established neighborhood and offers the perfect opportunity to create your dream home. The home boasts a spacious and well-thought-out floor plan, providing plenty of room for family living and entertaining. Each room holds the promise of transformation to match your unique style. Large windows throughout the home allow abundant natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen, though not updated, is functional and offers the opportunity for a custom renovation to suit your culinary preferences. The master bedroom features an ensuite half bath, providing convenience and privacy. Step outside to a generous backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or creating your private oasis. The potential for landscaping and outdoor improvements is limitless.
